<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/twstyles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        .faq-question::after {
            content: '+';
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .faq-question.active::after {
            content: '-';
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .faq-icon {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">

  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq">
    <div class="faq-header">
        <h1><%= header %></h1> 
        <input type="text" class="faq-search" placeholder="Search FAQs..." />
        <p><%= message %></p>

    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">What services do you offer?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                We offer a wide range of residential services to transform your living spaces. Our expert interior design services bring beauty and functionality together, while our exterior design solutions create stunning outdoor spaces that blend style and nature. Additionally, we provide comprehensive renovation services to revamp and modernize your spaces, tailored to your specific needs.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How can I get in touch with you?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">You can get in touch with us through our contact page or by emailing us at mj.interiordesignstudio@gmail.com.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">What is your pricing model?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Our pricing model varies depending on the project scope and requirements. Please contact us for a detailed quote.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Do you offer custom designs?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, we specialize in creating custom designs tailored to your specific needs and preferences.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How long does it take to complete a project?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">The duration of a project depends on its complexity and scope. We will provide a timeline after discussing your requirements.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">What is your refund policy?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">We offer a satisfaction guarantee. If you are not satisfied with our services, please contact us within 30 days for a refund.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Can I see samples of your work?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, you can view our portfolio on our website to see examples of our previous projects.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Do you offer support after the project is completed?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, we provide ongoing support and maintenance services to ensure your project continues to perform optimally.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">What payment methods do you accept?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">We accept various payment methods including cash, credit cards, and bank transfers.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Can I make changes to the design after the project is completed?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, we offer revision services to make changes to the design even after the project is completed. Please contact us for more details.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
